---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="定价 — AI Privacy Gateway | Lite 免费 · Pro ¥99/月 · Enterprise 定制"
  description="AI Privacy Gateway 提供三个版本：Lite 个人免费版（开源）、Pro 团队版 ¥99/月（20 人）、Enterprise 企业版（定制年费）。选择适合你的版本。"
  canonicalURL="https://privacygw.pages.dev/pricing">
  <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-1"></div>
  <div class="gradient-orb gradient-orb-2"></div>

  <!-- 导航栏 -->
  <nav class="nav glass">
    <div class="container nav-container">
      <div class="nav-brand">
        <span class="brand-icon">🔒</span>
        <span class="brand-text">Privacy Gateway</span>
      </div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/#features" class="nav-link">功能</a>
        <a href="/#how-it-works" class="nav-link">原理</a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="nav-link">定价</a>
        <a href="/download" class="btn btn-secondary">下载</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>选择你的版本</h1>
    <p>从个人到企业，为不同规模团队设计</p>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="pricing-container">
      <!-- Lite Version -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="pricing-header">
          <div class="tier-label">免费版</div>
          <h2>Lite</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-price">
          <span class="price">免费</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>正则脱敏（手机号/邮箱/身份证/银行卡）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>流式代理 + 缓冲区管理</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>自定义敏感词（手动添加）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>基础管理后台</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item disabled">
            <span class="cross">✗</span>
            <span>多人并发支持</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item disabled">
            <span class="cross">✗</span>
            <span>团队看板</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item disabled">
            <span class="cross">✗</span>
            <span>云端规则自动更新</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway" class="btn btn-outline">
          GitHub 下载
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Pro Version -->
      <div class="pricing-card popular">
        <div class="popular-badge">最受欢迎</div>
        <div class="pricing-header">
          <div class="tier-label">团队版</div>
          <h2>Pro</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-price">
          <span class="price">¥99</span>
          <span class="period">/月</span>
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-description">适合 20 人以下团队使用</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>全部 Lite 功能</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>多人并发（20 人）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>SQLite WAL 模式</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>团队看板 + 会话查询</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>云端规则自动更新</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>日/周/月统计报告</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>邮件技术支持</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="openCheckout('pro')">
          立即购买
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Enterprise Version -->
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <div class="pricing-header">
          <div class="tier-label">企业版</div>
          <h2>Enterprise</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-price">
          <span class="price">定制</span>
          <span class="period">年费</span>
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-description">适合大型企业部署</p>
        <ul class="pricing-features">
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>全部 Pro 功能</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>100+ 人高并发支持</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>Redis 集群存储</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>AC 自动机（万级词库）</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>审计日志 + 告警通知</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>权限控制 (RBAC)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="feature-item">
            <span class="check">✓</span>
            <span>驻场支持 + SLA 保障</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="mailto:contact@privacygw.com?subject=Enterprise%20咨询" class="btn btn-outline">
          联系我们
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="faq-container">
      <h3>常见问题</h3>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>购买后如何获取 License Key？</h4>
        <p>购买完成后，License Key 会发送到您的邮箱。在管理后台输入 Key 即可激活 Pro 版功能。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>支持退款吗？</h4>
        <p>支持 7 天无理由退款。如果您对产品不满意，请发送邮件至 support@privacygw.com。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>License 可以在多台机器使用吗？</h4>
        <p>Pro 版 License 绑定硬件指纹，支持最多 3 台设备轮换。如需更多设备，请联系我们升级。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-item">
        <h4>如何升级到 Enterprise 版？</h4>
        <p>请发送邮件至 contact@privacygw.com，我们会根据您的需求提供定制方案。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 购买弹窗 -->
  <div class="checkout-overlay" id="checkoutOverlay" style="display:none">
    <div class="checkout-modal glass">
      <button class="checkout-close" onclick="closeCheckout()">×</button>
      <h3 id="checkoutTitle">购买 Pro 版</h3>
      <p class="checkout-price" id="checkoutPrice">¥99/月</p>

      <!-- 步骤 1: 输入邮箱 -->
      <div id="checkoutStep1">
        <label class="checkout-label">邮箱地址（用于接收 License Key）</label>
        <input type="email" id="customerEmail" class="checkout-input" placeholder="your@email.com" required>
        <div class="checkout-methods">
          <button class="payment-method-btn active" onclick="selectPayment('paypal')" id="paypalTab">
            <span class="method-icon">💳</span> PayPal / 信用卡
          </button>
          <button class="payment-method-btn" onclick="selectPayment('wechat')" id="wechatTab">
            <span class="method-icon">💚</span> 微信支付
          </button>
        </div>

        <!-- PayPal 支付区域 -->
        <div id="paypalSection" class="payment-section">
          <div id="paypal-button-container" style="margin-top:1rem"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- 微信支付区域 -->
        <div id="wechatSection" class="payment-section" style="display:none">
          <div class="wechat-pay-info">
            <div class="wechat-qr-placeholder">
              <div class="qr-code-frame">
                <img src="/wechat-pay-qr.jpg" alt="微信支付收款码" width="220" height="220" loading="lazy" />
              </div>
              <p class="wechat-note">微信扫码支付 ¥99</p>
              <p class="wechat-instruction">支付完成后，请发送支付截图和接收邮箱至<br/><strong>lichengfei7@gmail.com</strong></p>
              <p class="wechat-manual">我们将在 24 小时内发送 License Key 到您的邮箱</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 步骤 2: 购买成功 -->
      <div id="checkoutStep2" style="display:none">
        <div class="success-icon">✅</div>
        <h4>购买成功！</h4>
        <p class="success-text">License Key 已发送到您的邮箱</p>
        <div class="license-display" id="licenseDisplay"></div>
        <p class="success-note">请检查收件箱（或垃圾邮件箱）</p>
        <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="closeCheckout()">关闭</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 页脚 -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-content">
      <div class="footer-brand">
        <span class="brand-icon">🔒</span>
        <span class="brand-text">Privacy Gateway</span>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/download">下载</a>
        <a href="/pricing">定价</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/gunxueqiu6/ai-privacy-gateway">GitHub</a>
        <a href="mailto:contact@privacygw.com">联系我们</a>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-copyright">
        © 2026 AI Privacy Gateway. MIT License.
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="https://www.paypal.com/sdk/js?client-id=AXO6jh-66p-C8s_kaBXq9JVQN4MVpHj5uZztJv-8k6ut5Z-B9c97BYBTtPxC90Uij1DT7cl0ytsPiukq&currency=CNY&intent=capture" async></script>
  <script>
    const LICENSE_SERVER = 'https://149.104.12.203:8443';
    let selectedTier = 'pro';
    let selectedPayment = 'paypal';

    function openCheckout(tier) {
      selectedTier = tier;
      const overlay = document.getElementById('checkoutOverlay');
      const title = document.getElementById('checkoutTitle');
      const price = document.getElementById('checkoutPrice');
      if (tier === 'pro') {
        title.textContent = '购买 Pro 版';
        price.textContent = '¥99/月';
      } else {
        title.textContent = '咨询 Enterprise 版';
        price.textContent = '定制年费';
      }
      document.getElementById('checkoutStep1').style.display = 'block';
      document.getElementById('checkoutStep2').style.display = 'none';
      overlay.style.display = 'flex';
      if (tier === 'pro' && selectedPayment === 'paypal') {
        setTimeout(renderPayPalButton, 200);
      }
    }

    function closeCheckout() {
      document.getElementById('checkoutOverlay').style.display = 'none';
    }

    function selectPayment(method) {
      selectedPayment = method;
      document.getElementById('paypalTab').classList.toggle('active', method === 'paypal');
      document.getElementById('wechatTab').classList.toggle('active', method === 'wechat');
      document.getElementById('paypalSection').style.display = method === 'paypal' ? 'block' : 'none';
      document.getElementById('wechatSection').style.display = method === 'wechat' ? 'block' : 'none';
      if (method === 'paypal') {
        setTimeout(renderPayPalButton, 200);
      }
    }

    function renderPayPalButton() {
      const container = document.getElementById('paypal-button-container');
      if (!container || typeof paypal === 'undefined') return;
      container.innerHTML = '';
      paypal.Buttons({
        style: { layout: 'vertical', color: 'gold', shape: 'rect', label: 'paypal' },
        createOrder: function(data, actions) {
          return actions.order.create({
            purchase_units: [{
              description: 'AI Privacy Gateway Pro — 月度订阅',
              amount: { currency_code: 'CNY', value: '99.00' }
            }]
          });
        },
        onApprove: function(data, actions) {
          const email = document.getElementById('customerEmail').value.trim();
          if (!email) {
            alert('请先输入邮箱地址');
            return;
          }
          // 调用 License Server 完成支付 + 生成 License
          fetch(`${LICENSE_SERVER}/api/payment/complete`, {
            method: 'POST',
            headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
            body: JSON.stringify({
              order_id: data.orderID,
              customer_email: email,
              tier: selectedTier,
              expires_in_days: 365,
              max_concurrent: 20
            })
          })
          .then(r => r.json())
          .then(result => {
            if (result.status === 'completed') {
              document.getElementById('checkoutStep1').style.display = 'none';
              document.getElementById('checkoutStep2').style.display = 'block';
              document.getElementById('licenseDisplay').textContent = result.license_key;
            } else {
              alert('支付验证失败，请联系 support@privacygw.com');
            }
          })
          .catch(err => {
            console.error('Payment completion error:', err);
            alert('网络错误，请稍后重试。如果已扣款，请联系 support@privacygw.com');
          });
        },
        onError: function(err) {
          console.error('PayPal error:', err);
          alert('PayPal 支付出错，请重试或选择其他支付方式');
        }
      }).render('#paypal-button-container');
    }

    document.getElementById('checkoutOverlay').addEventListener('click', function(e) {
      if (e.target === this) closeCheckout();
    });
  </script>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .pricing-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .pricing-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: var(--primary-dim);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .pricing-card.popular {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--primary-glow);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .popular-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-dim), var(--primary));
    color: white;
    padding: 4px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .tier-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-header h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-price {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pricing-price .price {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .pricing-price .period {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-description {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pricing-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .feature-item.disabled {
    opacity: 0.5;
    text-decoration: line-through;
  }

  .check, .cross {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .check {
    background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
    color: #22c55e;
  }

  .cross {
    background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.1);
    color: #ef4444;
  }

  .faq-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-container h3 {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item h4 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 1rem 0;
  }

  .nav-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .nav-brand {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .brand-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .brand-text {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .nav-link {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .footer {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .footer-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-links a {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .footer-links a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .footer-copyright {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .pricing-container {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pricing-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .pricing-card.popular {
      transform: none;
    }
  }

  /* 购买弹窗 */
  .checkout-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    z-index: 200;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .checkout-modal {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
    max-height: 90vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .checkout-close {
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem;
    right: 1rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    cursor: pointer;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .checkout-close:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }

  .checkout-modal h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .checkout-price {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .checkout-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .checkout-input {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--bg-base);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .checkout-input:focus {
    border-color: var(--primary);
  }

  .checkout-methods {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .payment-method-btn {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: var(--bg-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .payment-method-btn.active {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--primary);
    background: var(--primary-bg, rgba(79, 209, 149, 0.1));
  }

  .method-icon { margin-right: 0.25rem; }

  .payment-section { margin-top: 0.5rem; }

  .wechat-qr-placeholder {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .qr-code-frame {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 12px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .wechat-note {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .wechat-instruction {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
